Determines whether two specified instances of [`PlistHandle`](../PlistHandle.md) are not equal.

```csharp
public static bool operator !=(PlistHandle value1, PlistHandle value2)
```

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| value1 | The first pointer or handle to compare. |
| value2 | The second pointer or handle to compare. |

## Return Value
